{"tid":50900,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"甲鐵城卡巴内里真人舞台劇!","createTime":"2016-12-22T19:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T19:54:21.000Z","uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fbe15dd6cf1682489cb368d9cb9d552dff1fe61","tid":50900,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/48/97/q5iZn6GVlaCXqqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F48%2F97%2Fq5iZn6GVlaCXqqo.jpg&h=c17d57cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n進入甲鐵城的世界吧！你自認才智過人，想嘗試遭遇卡巴內、面對困境，並與生駒、無名等人一起動腦解決問題嗎？或是只想當一位身歷其境的觀眾呢？新型態舞台體驗「舞台&times;逃脫遊戲 2.5 Escape Stage《甲鐵城的卡巴內里》」將於1月6日於東京上演，我們快來看看真人版的無名、菖蒲以及其他角色們的定裝照吧！<br />\n原汁原味的內容在這裡<br />\n生駒（伊崎龍次郎　飾演）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/48/97/q5iZn6GVlaCXqqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F48%2F97%2Fq5iZn6GVlaCXqqQ.jpg&h=513a1684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無名（高橋紗妃　飾演）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/48/97/q5iZn6GVlaCXqqU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F48%2F97%2Fq5iZn6GVlaCXqqU.jpg&h=d570187e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0adfb786094ae229a23884f7bd9fbad06451fb7","tid":50900,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:23:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ef83d3eb0982d722d1d34bef9b582d489df0392","tid":50900,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:26:50.000Z","msg":"菖蒲（小瀬田麻由　飾演）<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/48/97/q5iZn6GVlaCXqqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F48%2F97%2Fq5iZn6GVlaCXqqY.jpg&h=82df0d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來棲（財木琢磨　飾演）<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/48/97/q5iZn6GVlaCXqqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F48%2F97%2Fq5iZn6GVlaCXqqc.jpg&h=96d24284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公演內容由兩大部分構成<br />\n分別為60分鐘的解謎歷程以及20分鐘的舞台演出。在解謎的部分，分為可以參與逃脫歷程的觀眾與只能觀看的觀眾（在票價上有所差異），參與逃脫遊戲的觀眾每個人都可進入卡巴內肆虐的世界，並成為甲鐵城的一員，協助主要角色們完成任務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/48/97/q5iZn6GVlaCXqqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F48%2F97%2Fq5iZn6GVlaCXqqk.jpg&h=45375931&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c142580dbdb5a8d340780a200f64b75253000238","tid":50900,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i6h45mav\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi6h45mav&h=f89911c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sb061zw4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsb061zw4&h=bbb1ab09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u6p5rcx8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu6p5rcx8&h=2a5a5742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0xsfa3d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0xsfa3d1&h=6db2a6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yp8vnxwg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyp8vnxwg&h=a9ed5ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yik8ezqf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyik8ezqf&h=7dad3ace&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caf71ed91882e3c8e120a0aef07ac2cd807a72f8","tid":50900,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T19:44:34.000Z","msg":"無名唔夠靚 菖蒲成個男人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{